{{wikipedia}}
==English==

===Adjective===
'''anonymous'''
# Wanting a [[name]]; not named and determined, as an animal not assigned to any species.
# Without any name [[acknowledge]]d, as that of author, contributor, or the like: as, an anonymous pamphlet; an anonymous benefactor; an anonymous subscription.
# Of unknown name; whose name is [[withhold|withheld]]: as, an anonymous author.

